{"word":"ἐκμηρύομαι","slug":"ἐκμηρύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκμηρύομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to wind out like a ball of thread</i>: of an army, <i>to make</i> it <i>defile out</i> of a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a>, of the army, <i>to defile</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}